name: The Rosebery Dining Table
description: This award-winning luxury round Rosebery dining table is a sublime example of contemporary British craftsmanship at its best. Finished in a striking contrast of high gloss sycamore and dazzling gold leaf it is no surprise that it has won awards for its stunning allure. The table top boasts an eye-catching radial pattern sitting on a captstan shaped base that has been hand gilded to shimmering perfection. Choose from a varied selection of beautiful finishes and three beautiful shades of gold offering something for those that prefer cooler silvery tones and those that prefer warmer golden tones. The Rosebery Dining Table would sit perfectly in any sumptuous setting where the requirement is to make a grand statement of mesmerising design.
